{"tid":2205023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[慢慢周]報道指華為透過香港星美技術隱瞞巴西業務","createTime":"2020-09-16T13:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T07:34:18.000Z","uid":51271,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0f8b09de9a8ddb36a39d36820b8ffd6fe2b84198","tid":2205023,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T13:12:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549983-20200916.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549983-20200916.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2Br2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=2152c9f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549983-20200916.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=18becb70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549983-20200916.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n《路透社》報道，被指是中國電信設備生產商華為用作逃避美國制裁，向伊朗提供美國設備的香港星美技術，也隱瞞同巴西有業務往來，相信為美國控告華為及引渡副董事長孟晚舟提供有力支持。<br />\n<br />\n華為被指透過星美，在2007至2014年與伊朗交易，華為聲稱在2007年已出售星美。<br />\n<br />\n但《路透社》發現，根據在聖保羅的公司紀錄，華為出售星美後的五年，仍然關係密切。兩名華為高層－胡厚崑和郭平，直至2007年底仍然同星美有關。星美在2002至2012年涉足巴西，收購華為巴西分公司少量股權，胡厚崑2002年5月調到聖保羅擔任經理。<br />\n<br />\n胡厚崑之後離開，但他同郭平在2007年擔任華為在香港的另一間分公司董事，公司擁有星美，兩人和孟晚舟是公司的董事。公司之後把星美出售。<br />\n<br />\n美國當局聲稱，華為從未放棄對星美的控制。"},{"pid":"243b29dd6aecd79eb0b4a1282bdea2348ded151b","tid":2205023,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T13:14:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c4ef77d1d0013bd46e55cb26ba0fc49887dd4a","tid":2205023,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T14:17:40.000Z","msg":"香港白手套"},{"pid":"0813e4ddcf839ce6fac9bd3f957f00a3709e3513"